OL,3,CElle Edwards murder: Gunman loses
OL,4,Cappeal against prison sentence
OL,6,FThe gunman who shot dead a 26-year-old
OL,7,Fbeautician outside a pub on Christmas
OL,8,FEve 2022 has lost his appeal against
OL,9,Fhis .
OL,11,FConor Chapman, 23, was convicted of
OL,12,Fmurdering , hitting her twice in the
OL,13,Fback of the head, when he fired 12
OL,14,Fshots from a Skorpion submachine gun
OL,15,Foutside the Lighthouse pub in ,
OL,16,FMerseyside.
OL,18,FFive other people were also injured in
OL,19,Fthe shooting, with Chapman intending
OL,20,Fto murder two men - Jake Duffy and
OL,21,FKieran Salkeld.
