OL,3,CElle Edwards murder: Gunman loses
OL,4,Cappeal against prison sentence
OL,6,FChapman appealed against his sentence
OL,7,Flength - but, at the Court of Appeal
OL,8,Fon 29 February, senior judges rejected
OL,9,Fhis challenge.
OL,11,FThe Lady Chief Justice Baroness Carr,
OL,12,Fwho considered the case alongside Mrs
OL,13,FJustice May and Mr Justice Foxton,
OL,14,Fsaid they concluded the sentence was
OL,15,F"severe, but not manifestly excessive".
