OL,3,CElle Edwards murder: Gunman loses
OL,4,Cappeal against prison sentence
OL,6,FBaroness Carr said that in a bid for
OL,7,Frevenge, Chapman was "utterly
OL,8,Findifferent to who else might be or
OL,9,Fwould be killed or injured in the
OL,10,Fprocess", adding it was clear on the
OL,11,Fnight "many bystanders were present
OL,12,Fcelebrating the holiday season" in the
OL,13,Fpub.
OL,15,FThe judge said Chapman "killed a
OL,16,Fperson with murderous intent" amid
OL,17,F"intending to kill two more", adding:
OL,18,F"This was a case in which in his
OL,19,Fobsessive determination to take those
OL,20,Ftwo lives, (he) was willing to kill
OL,21,Fmore and could so easily have done so."
