OL,3,CElle Edwards murder: Gunman loses
OL,4,Cappeal against prison sentence
OL,6,FMr Rhind said: "As bad as this
OL,7,Foffending is, the court will in the
OL,8,Ffuture have to deal with more serious
OL,9,Fcases and a minimum term in this case
OL,10,Fof 48 years leaves no room those even
OL,11,Fmore serious cases that do not require
OL,12,Fa whole life term."
OL,14,FHe also argued Chapman's young age at
OL,15,Fthe time of the offences provided a
OL,16,F"small degree of mitigation" and said
OL,17,Fhis was "not a case which involved a
OL,18,Fsubstantial degree of premeditation or
OL,19,Fplanning".
