OL,3,CElle Edwards murder: Gunman loses
OL,4,Cappeal against prison sentence
OL,6,FThe court heard that since Chapman's
OL,7,Farrest, there had been no firearm
OL,8,Fdischarges in the Wirral, while
OL,9,Fdischarges in Merseyside generally had
OL,10,Ffallen from 49 in 2022 to 23 in 2023 `
OL,11,Fthe lowest figure for 20 years.
OL,13,F"Merseyside Police identify the
OL,14,Fcircumstances and the sentencing in
OL,15,Fthis case as having had a significant
OL,16,Fdeterrent effect," Mr Power said.
