OL,3,CElle Edwards murder: Gunman loses
OL,4,Cappeal against prison sentence
OL,6,FChapman's trial at Liverpool Crown
OL,7,FCourt in 2023 was told the shooting
OL,8,Fwas said to be the result of a gang
OL,9,Ffeud on the Wirral, where there had
OL,10,Fbeen nine shootings in 2022.
OL,12,FAt his sentencing last summer, Mr
OL,13,FJustice Goose said what Chapman did
OL,14,F"was as wicked as it was shocking",
OL,15,Fadding the offender was a "highly
OL,16,Fdangerous man".
